value:
Hey, your weapon shoots things.
Mine too... It's like we're twins.

I serve Lady Hinoka. She's strong...
and kind...and really nice. I like
her lots and lots.

On patrol, huh? Watch out for traps.
Or you'll fall into one.$k$pWait... Am I in a trap now?

We should go hunting. We'll step into
a trap, I bet. But you can just
summon Lady Hinoka to save us.

When I practice at the range here,
I nearly hit some guy named Alfonse.
Usually, anyway. The face he makes!

...$Nu?$k$pOh, good. I'm here to tell you...
uh...? Yeah. Hi. Your friend
$Nf sent me.
I'm doing well...
Woo-hoo.

Yay. Wait, that wasn't much,
was it?

One step closer to...uh, not
stepping into more traps.

I'm Setsuna from the Kingdom of
Hoshido. I'm good with bows.
And, uh...falling into traps?

Woo-hoo. It's you, Summoner.
You going to do more of
that summoning thing today?$k$pI like a crowd. It's nice. And more
of us means more people around
to help if I fall into a trap.$k$pThat happens all the time,
you know. Have I ever
mentioned it?$k$pBut you know, more of us also
means you have less time
for me. Sad.$k$pWhat? You promise you won't
forget about me? What?
You never could?$k$pYay. I feel the same. Are you
sure we're not the same person?
It wouldn't surprise me at all!
えい…
Here we go...
うあっ…
You got me...
I won't lose!
There we go...
Hey, you're my prey!
Look, a butterfly.
Oh man...
Heehee
Fun times. Good ones too. Every day is a happy day.
I'm in a pit. Oh, no, no. Not now. I mean later, when you can't find me.
You'll help me if I fall into a trap, right?
I love hunting. Anything, really. But little buggies most of all.
I popped out of a divine weapon? Woo-hoo. Always wanted to do that.
Where is Lady Hinoka? She'll totally help if I fall into a trap.
They say I'm a daydreamer. Works for me.
Sure...
Yay...
Where now?
